```{r}
pacman::p_load(tidyverse)
```
### Loading data
```{r}
results <- read_csv("./output/model_results.csv")
```
## Plot the results nicely
```{r}
results %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x=num_params, y=f1, color=model)) + 
  geom_point(size=5) + 
  ylim(0.5, 1) + 
  theme_minimal()
```
